        <updateDate>2014-11-21T18:55:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Sandy Reinvestment Extension Act of 2014 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the&nbsp;nonrecognition of gain from property involuntarily converted,&nbsp;to extend from two years to five years the replacement period for property involuntarily converted in the Hurricane Sandy Disaster Area. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
